title: BRIEF-Fannie Mae Announces Sale Of Non-Performing Loans
text: 43 PM / in 13 minutes BRIEF-Fannie Mae Announces Sale Of Non-Performing Loans Reuters Staff Feb 13 (Reuters) - The Federal National Mortgage Association : * FANNIE MAE ANNOUNCES SALE OF NON-PERFORMING LOANS * FANNIE MAE - ANNOUNCED LATEST SALE OF NON-PERFORMING LOANS, INCLUDING COâ€˜S ELEVENTH AND TWELFTH COMMUNITY IMPACT POOLS * FANNIE MAE - THE THREE LARGER POOLS INCLUDE ABOUT 5,900 LOANS TOTALING $1.04 BILLION IN UNPAID PRINCIPAL BALANCE * FANNIE MAE - THE THREE LARGER POOLS ALSO INCLUDE COMMUNITY IMPACT POOLS OF APPROXIMATELY 190 LOANS TOTALING $35.68 MILLION IN UPB Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
